# Normalize line endings to LF for files that matter to Linux-based tooling
# (GitHub Actions runs on ubuntu-latest; CRLF inside a multi-line `run:`
# block can break shell execution there). Without this, Windows editors/
# GitHub Desktop can silently reintroduce CRLF on save.

* text=auto eol=lf

*.yml text eol=lf
*.yaml text eol=lf
*.sh text eol=lf
